     -> neighbor 192.0.2.1 local-as 99 no-prepend
        -> "local-as" will not be added to the AS_PATH.

     -> neighbor 192.0.2.1 local-as 99 no-prepend replace-as
        -> Replace real AS with local AS in the eBGP updates.
